variables.description: The interval for publishing access logs in minutes. You can specify an interval                   of either 5 minutes or 60 minutes.
variables.name: EmitInterval

variables.description: Whether logging is enabled for the load balancer.
variables.name: Enabled

variables.description: The name of an Amazon S3 bucket where access log files are stored.
variables.name: S3BucketName

variables.description: A prefix for the all log object keys, such as                      my-load-balancer-logs/prod. If you store log files from multiple                   sources in a single bucket, you can use a prefix to distinguish each log file and                   its source.
variables.name: S3BucketPrefix
